product_name: Keen Bailey Slip-On Shoes - Women's - 2012 Closeout
long_description: Walk the dog or brave your cold-weather commute in the Keen Bailey Slip-On Shoes. Warm, waterproof uppers offer total protection while easy, slip-on style allows quick entry and exit. Nubuck leather uppers with KEEN.DRY(TM) waterproof, breathable membranes keep feet dry without letting them overheat. Faux-fur linings provide reliable warmth in cold conditions. Molded EVA midsoles deliver all-day support and cushioning. Keen Bailey Slip-On Shoes feature dual-climate rubber outsoles that harden in the cold, providing great traction in packed snow and ice. Closeout.
